@token = paste-your-jwt-token-here

### Get all items
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items/search

###

### Search with filters
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items/search?type=lost&category=Electronics&keyword=phone

###

### Create lost item (requires auth)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/items/lost
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: BEARER {{token}}

{
  "title": "Lost iPhone 13",
  "category": "Electronics",
  "description": "Black iPhone 13 with a cracked screen protector lost near the library",
  "date": "2025-01-15T10:00:00Z",
  "location": "Cairo University, Giza, Egypt"
}

###

### Get single item
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items/ITEM_ID_HERE

###

### Get my items
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items/my
Authorization: BEARER {{token}}

###

### Get nearby items
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items/nearby?lat=30.0444&lng=31.2357&radius=5
